f<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-left kksr-valign-top\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;3243&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;9&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 post&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;5\\\/5 - (9 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;138&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"3\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"4\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"5\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-active\" style=\"width: 138px;\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n                \n\n<div class=\"kksr-legend\" style=\"font-size: 19.2px;\">\n            5\/5 - (9 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #d83131;\">GIA S\u01af TO\u00c1N GI\u1eceI &#8211; CHUY\u00caN S\u01af PH\u1ea0M &#8211; D\u1ea0Y T\u01af DUY H\u1eccC TO\u00c1N<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC SINH KH\u00d4NG HI\u1ec2U B\u00c0I<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">\u00a0<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/demogiasu.vntsc.vn\/uploads\/news\/Gia-Su-Cac-Mon\/Sinh-Hoc\/hot_2.gif\" alt=\"\" \/> Hotline: 0963.138.511 &#8211; 0862.856.500<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n gi\u1ecfi, c\u00f3 nghi\u00eap v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc t\u01b0 duy logic, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ecdi nhu c\u1ea7u h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh t\u1eeb l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u01a1n b\u1ea3n t\u1edbi luy\u1ec7n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, h\u1ecdc n\u00e2ng cao, chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea5p, \u00f4n thi \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc, Luy\u1ec7n thi cam k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"I_%E2%80%93_HINH_THUC_GIA_SU_DAY_KEM_MON_TOAN\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>I<\/strong>\u00a0&#8211;\u00a0<b>H\u00ccNH TH\u1ee8C GIA S\u01af D\u1ea0Y K\u00c8M M\u00d4N TO\u00c1N<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">D\u1ea1y k\u00e8m\u00a0<b>1 gia s\u01b0<\/b>\u00a0\u2013\u00a0<b>1 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/b>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t (C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc k\u00e8m nh\u00f3m t\u1eeb 2-5 em h\u1ecdc sinh)<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">H\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh (Ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc nh\u00e0 gia s\u01b0 do gia \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh)<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Ph\u1ee5 huynh, h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u01b0a ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0: Sinh vi\u00ean hay gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, H\u1ecdc kh\u1ed1i ng\u00e0nh, tr\u01b0\u1eddng, qu\u00ea qu\u00e1n, gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh\u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc tu\u1ef3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gia s\u01b0 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc:<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">+ T\u1eeb l\u1edbp 1 &#8211; 3 : 1h30p\/bu\u1ed5i ( \u0110\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t)<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">+ L\u1edbp 5 -12: 2h\/bu\u1ed5i ( \u0110\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t)<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"II_%E2%80%93_GIA_SU_MON_TOAN_SINH_VIEN_GIAO_VIEN_LA_AI\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><b>II &#8211; GIA S\u01af M\u00d4N TO\u00c1N: SINH VI\u00caN, GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN L\u00c0 AI?<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Gia_su_la_giao_vien\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong>???? Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean: <\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean \u0111ang c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, trung t\u00e2m d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean t\u1ef1 do chuy\u00ean \u0111i d\u1ea1y gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m. C\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u1edbp s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n, y\u00eau th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc h\u01a1n<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Gia_su_la_sinh_vien\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong>???? Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean: <\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n<\/strong> l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean kh\u1ed1i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0: \u0110H S\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m, \u0110H Qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0110H B\u00e1ch khoa, \u0110H Lu\u1eadt, \u0110H Kinh t\u1ebf qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n, \u0110H Y, \u0110H D\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110H Khoa h\u1ecdc t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean\u2026. C\u00e1c gia s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh Minh \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, \u0111i\u1ec3m thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc m\u00f4n To\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u00ean 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1513\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1513\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1513\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-la-ai-300x212.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-la-ai-300x212.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-la-ai.png 748w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1513\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><em>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"III_%E2%80%93_BANG_GIA_HOC_PHI_GIA_SU_TOAN_TAI_NHA_O_HA_NOI\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>III &#8211; B\u1ea2NG GI\u00c1, H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af TO\u00c1N T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0 \u1ede H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><i><br \/>\n<h2 id=\"tablepress-17-name\" class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-17\">H\u1eccC PH\u00cd - GIA S\u01af TO\u00c1N T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-17\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-17 tbody-has-connected-cells\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-17-name\">\n<tbody class=\"row-striping row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"column-1\">L\u1edaP H\u1eccC<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">SINH VI\u00caN<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\n\t<td class=\"column-2\">1 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">2 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">1 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">2 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 1<\/td><td class=\"column-2\"> 100.000 \u2013 130.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">150.000 \u2013 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\"> 200.000 - 250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 \u2013 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 2<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">120.000 - 150.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">150.000 - 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">200.000 - 250.000\t<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 - 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 3<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">130.000 - 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u00d4n thi \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">200.000 - 250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">350.000 - 400.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\"><br \/>\n\u00d4n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, HS chuy\u00ean<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-17 from cache --><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i, h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tu\u1ef3 theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 hotline: <span style=\"\">096.31.38.511<\/span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam: H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed m\u00f4n <a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-3000-gia-su-tieng-anh-tai-nha-tang-hieu-qua-gap-5-lan\/\"><b>gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfng anh <\/b><\/a>update m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem ngay <a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-gia-su-hoa-gioi-o-ha-noi-tu-lop-8-12-chi-tu-100k\/\"><b>Gia s\u01b0 Ho\u00e1 <\/b><\/a>cho con h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t, b\u1edbt m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IV_%E2%80%93_NEN_THUE_GIA_SU_LA_SINH_VIEN_HAY_GIAO_VIEN\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><b>IV &#8211; N\u00caN THU\u00ca GIA S\u01af L\u00c0 SINH VI\u00caN HAY GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN?<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb ph\u1ee5 huynh \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t ra. Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh \u0111\u01b0a ra t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong>???? Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean To\u00e1n:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><em>+ L\u1ee3i \u00edch:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u1edbp<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u00fang, \u0111\u01b0a ra ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc sinh<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">N\u1eafm b\u1eaft t\u00e2m l\u00fd h\u1ecdc sinh t\u1ed1t, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><em>+ H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed cao ( Dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 200.000-300.000 VN\u0110)<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Th\u1eddi gian k\u00e9m linh ho\u1ea1t<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">\u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh n\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch th\u00edch h\u1ecdc b\u1eb1ng sinh vi\u00ean<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1515\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1515\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1515\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nen-thue-gia-su-la-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-300x235.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"470\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nen-thue-gia-su-la-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-300x235.jpg 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nen-thue-gia-su-la-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien.jpg 660w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1515\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><em>N\u00ean thu\u00ea gia s\u01b0 to\u00e1n l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean hay gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong>???? Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><em>+ L\u1ee3i \u00edch:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed r\u1ebb<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">D\u1ec5 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 y\u00eau th\u00edch m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc cho h\u1ecdc sinh<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Th\u1eddi gian linh ho\u1ea1t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y ng\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c t\u1ed1i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i B\u00ecnh Minh l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2 tr\u1edf l\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y cho c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Do \u0111\u00f3, tu\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a em h\u1ecdc sinh v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kinh t\u1ebf gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00ean thu\u00ea gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean hay gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"V_%E2%80%93_05_DIEU_CHA_ME_NEN_LAM_KHI_THUE_GIA_SU\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>V &#8211; 05 \u0110I\u1ec0U CHA M\u1eb8 N\u00caN L\u00c0M KHI THU\u00ca GIA S\u01af<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li2\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #333399;\"><strong>X\u00e1c \u0111inh r\u00f5 l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a con<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Cha m\u1eb9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t. Cha m\u1eb9 c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft con y\u1ebfu ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 to\u00e1n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho con.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li2\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #333399;\"><strong>T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng tin gia s\u01b0<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, b\u1edfi hi\u1ec7n nay, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 trung t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng trung t\u00e2m c\u00f3 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng trung th\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng tin <strong>gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y to\u00e1n<\/strong>. C\u00f3 1 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p trung t\u00e2m th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t gia s\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i ho\u1eb7c sinh vi\u00ean t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u00edt khi s\u1ea3y ra.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1516\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1516\" style=\"width: 464px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1516\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/the_sinh_vien-232x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"464\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/the_sinh_vien-232x300.jpg 232w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/the_sinh_vien.jpg 665w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 464px) 100vw, 464px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1516\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><em>Ki\u1ec3m tra th\u00f4ng tin gia s\u01b0, th\u1ebb sinh vi\u00ean<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li2\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #333399;\"><strong>Tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 trong bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Cha m\u1eb9 c\u1ea7n d\u00e0nh ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u1ed3i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0. \u0110i\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t n\u00ean h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng tin gia s\u01b0 (th\u1ebb sinh vi\u00ean, CMT\u2026)<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Th\u1ee9 2 n\u00ean trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a con c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a con. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u0103n c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 gia s\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li2\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #333399;\"><strong>Ki\u1ec3m tra c\u00e1ch d\u1ea1y<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Cha m\u1eb9 kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ng\u1ed3i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp xem <strong>gia s\u01b0<\/strong> d\u1ea1y con h\u1ecdc trong c\u1ea3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean c\u1ea3 gia s\u01b0 v\u00e0 con. Nh\u01b0ng cha m\u1eb9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00f3 m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 gia s\u01b0 v\u00e0 con h\u1ecdc. \u0110\u1ec3 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o, cha m\u1eb9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e2u l\u00e2u mang n\u01b0\u1edbc hay hoa qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0o m\u1eddi gia s\u01b0. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1eeba th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a con.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li2\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #333399;\"><strong>B\u00e1o c\u00e1o ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Cha m\u1eb9 n\u00ean y\u00eau c\u1ea7u gia s\u01b0 cho con l\u00e0m b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a con.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 V\u1edbi 7 n\u0103m trong d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0, s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u01a1n 5000+ <strong>gia s\u01b0 to\u00e1n gi\u1ecfi<\/strong>, trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh cam k\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">G\u1ecdi ngay Hotline: <span style=\"\">096.31.38.511<\/span> ho\u1eb7c <span style=\"\">0862.856.500<\/span> ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n 24\/7 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a con b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #3366ff;\">Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top1-gia-su-van-ha-noi-bang-gia-mon-van-moi-nhat-2018\/\"><strong> Gia s\u01b0 V\u0103n<\/strong><\/a> t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 cho con chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef3 thi t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; N\u1ebfu anh ch\u1ecb c\u00f2n ch\u00e1u nh\u1ecf \u0111ang h\u1ecdc ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u201c B\u00ed k\u00edp ch\u1ecdn<a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/\"><strong> gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc<\/strong><\/a> chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c m\u1eb9 chia s\u1ebb \u201c<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #d83131;\"><b>TRUNG T\u00c2M\u00a0GIA S\u01af\u00a0B\u00ccNH MINH<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 1: N03, S\u1ed1 38-40 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u00fd Ki\u00ean, C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 2: 583 Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u00e3i, Thanh Xu\u00e2n, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 3: 479 L\u0129nh Nam, Ho\u00e0ng Mai, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p2\"><b>==&gt; Hotline (24\/7): 096.31.38.511 \u2013 0862.856.500<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GIA S\u01af TO\u00c1N GI\u1eceI &#8211; CHUY\u00caN S\u01af PH\u1ea0M &#8211; D\u1ea0Y T\u01af DUY H\u1eccC TO\u00c1N D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC SINH KH\u00d4NG HI\u1ec2U [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3464,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[478],"tags":[287,286],"class_list":["post-3243","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-gia-su-mon-toan-mb","tag-cach-day-tre-bi-benh-tu-ki","tag-cach-day-tre-tu-ki"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>[B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1] Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n gi\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 - D\u1ea1y con t\u01b0 duy h\u1ecdc To\u00e1n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Gia s\u01b0 to\u00e1n gi\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i h\u00e0 n\u1ed9i, gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh c\u00e1ch t\u01b0 duy t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc m\u00f4n to\u00e1n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, d\u1ea1y t\u1eeb c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00e2ng cao theo m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-mon-toan\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"C\u00e1ch d\u1ea1y tr\u1ebb t\u1ef1 k\u1ec9 - \u0110\u1ec3 con \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0T\u1ef1 k\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd \u0111ang b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb em. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh lo l\u1eafng c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 con t\u1ef1 k\u1ec9. Nhi\u1ec1u b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch d\u1ea1y tr\u1ebb t\u1ef1 k\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. B\u1eb1ng k\u1ecbnh ngh\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 quan s\u00e1t th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n, trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u1ee3i \u00fd c\u00e1ch d\u1ea1y tr\u1ebb b\u1ecb t\u1ef1 k\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 huynh tham kh\u1ea3o, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e1ch d\u1ea1y con \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-mon-toan\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2020-08-18T11:41:28+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2021-01-16T09:34:00+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Foto-ni\u00f1o.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"600\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"320\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:type\" content=\"image\/jpeg\" \/>\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"B\u00ecnh Minh\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:label1\" content=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft b\u1edfi\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data1